1.0.name: wordpress/wp-google-analytics-events
1.0.description: The WP Google Analytics Events plugin allows you to send events to Google Analytics for scrolling or clicking elements on the page. For example, create a Google Analytics event when a visitor scrolled down and viewed your pricing table. Did a user play a video? Create an event for that.
